						               													<description>The Apalpador and his friends are organizing a big &amp;quot;magosto&amp;quot; so they need to go out into the woods to look for chestnuts. Who will get more? In this game for the whole family you must use your favorite characters on each round to be the player who collects the most chestnuts and get the title of Master Chestnut.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player will draw cards from the deck to collect as many chestnuts as possible before three hedgehogs appear among their collection. The cards show chestnuts or hedgehogs. The player draws cards until his turn is over, when the player decides to stop drawing them or three hedgehogs have appeared. In the first case, the player will choose one of those cards for his reserve; on the other hand, in the second, he will lose all the cards that he has obtained.&amp;#10;The player with the most chestnuts at the end of the game will be the winner of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
